1.演者の初期配置
2.演出開始

It was a great honor to be entrusted with the task of
defeating demons by the goddess Actina.

I am truly blessed to have received the divine blessing of
Actina, the eldest daughter who has been trained by me!

It was an honor to be able to be by your side, the light of
the goddess Imiserinos.

We are truly blessed to have received the divine blessing of
Imiserinos, the eldest daughter. We will forever be able to
converse together!

Goddess Deirei's Shadow: 'Hey, hey, did you forget that I
was the one who picked her up?'

Goddess Deirei's Shadow: It feels like you're the one who
received the blessing of Deirei, the eldest daughter, who I,
the shadow of Goddess Deirei, set my eyes on!
Hero: What should I do next?

Actina, the shining goddess: 'You shall remain on the earth
and destroy what the demons have left behind.'

Goddess Imiserinos' Candle: Now that we have fulfilled our
duties as goddesses, we must leave the earth.

Goddess Deirei's Shadow: Hahaha, that's right, the earth
belongs to you humans now that we, the goddesses, have
departed.

Goddess Deirei's Shadow: Well, don't worry, I have left
behind a few souvenirs for you.

The era when the goddesses existed on Earth is later
referred to as the era of the three goddesses. And then,
both the demons and the goddesses disappeared, and the era
of humans began.

Humans, with the power of the given miracles and magic, will
proceed to regenerate the devastated world.

There certainly existed a place for the hero there. It was
the remnants of the malicious demons, cleverly hidden like
cancer cells. The role was to bury them and eradicate their
malice.

However, that's all. There is no place for the hero in the
rural areas, the royal palace, the taverns, or the common
houses.

An existence only for the sake of a role. An existence with
only things left to do. Even the hero, whose emotions had
almost disappeared, murmurs softly.
The goddesses are so selfish.
